#18 Hypoalbuminemia
We will recheck this as well as a total protein.
Spent 120 minutes with Mrs. Prime, her two sons, and her daughter.  Long discussion and reviewed 30+ pages of outside medical records.  I will see them back after her evaluation with one of our surgeons to discuss in more detail the advantages and risks of proceeding and what her risks are from a cardiac and medical perspective.  Will not put her on the surgical list at this time.  All questions were answered.
